postponed until next Saturday, May 6.  Listed below are the updates since the 
last memo:

BOOK-SPLIT

Completed
Position report which presents peak/off-peak volumes by month, by desk was 
delivered to Paul and Gregor
Deal summaries which support the position report were also delivered
