I hope that things went well in Calgary.  I am rapping things up here and I 
cannot wait to return home.  

My tentative meeting with Joe Gold for this afternoon has been rescheduled 
for 9:00 this morning.  Attached is my assessment of the Continental Power 
operations which I intend to discuss with him.  The first page is for Joe in 
